:: Enumerates a chain of records linked by next. in db.
++  enum
  |=  next/@sd
  ^-  (list @sd)
  =|  out/(list @sd)
  |-
  ?:  =(next -1)
    (flop out)
  =+  obj=(~(got by records.db) next)
  $(next next.obj, out [i=next t=out])

